00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:33,000
 I'm like, "Okay. What do you want to go and do?

674
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:35,000
 Do you want to go see the culture of Mexico?

675
00:42:35,000 --> 00:42:37,000
 Or do you want to go see Mayan ruins?

676
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:39,000
 Do you want to go to Coba, Tulum?

677
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:41,000
 Or you could go to Ixcadet.

678
00:42:41,000 --> 00:42:44,000
 It's like this kind of Mexican Disney World.

679
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:47,000
 Or do you want zip lines?

680
00:42:47,000 --> 00:42:49,000
 Because we could go to explore.

681
00:42:49,000 --> 00:42:51,000
 It's some of the best zip lines I've seen.

682
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:53,000
 Or, oh, there's these cenotes right where you're staying.

683
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:55,000
 A cenote is like an underground river

684
00:42:55,000 --> 00:42:57,000
 where you get in this tube,

685
00:42:57,000 --> 00:42:59,000
 and you go through this river that's underground

686
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:01,000
 and you get stalactites and stalagmites.

687
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:03,000
 Oh, one of my favorite places, Elena,

688
00:43:03,000 --> 00:43:05,000
 is Islamu Harris.

689
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:07,000
 It's a 30-minute ferry ride from Cancun

690
00:43:07,000 --> 00:43:09,000
 where you're getting off.

691
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:11,000
 You're going to be right there by the airport.

692
00:43:11,000 --> 00:43:13,000
 It's a $6 ferry ride. You get on the ferry.

693
00:43:13,000 --> 00:43:15,000
 You go to Islamu Harris.

694
00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:17,000
 It's where the Corona commercial was filmed,

695
00:43:17,000 --> 00:43:19,000
 if you've seen that. Beautiful beach, the sugar white sand,

696
00:43:19,000 --> 00:43:21,000
 the clear water, Islamu Harris.

697
00:43:21,000 --> 00:43:23,000
 You can take a golf cart.

698
00:43:23,000 --> 00:43:25,000
 What do you want to do?"

699
00:43:25,000 --> 00:43:27,000
 She'd be crazy not to talk to me.

