 Lots of times, as a foreigner,

702
00:43:31,000 --> 00:43:33,000
 I know what to do.

703
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:35,000
 I know what not to do.

704
00:43:35,000 --> 00:43:39,000
 If you're going to endure this world,

705
00:43:39,000 --> 00:43:41,000
 you would be

706
00:43:41,000 --> 00:43:43,000
 out of your mind

707
00:43:43,000 --> 00:43:45,000
 not to spend

708
00:43:45,000 --> 00:43:47,000
 intentional time

709
00:43:47,000 --> 00:43:49,000
 with Jesus,

710
00:43:49,000 --> 00:43:51,000
 knowing His Word,

711
00:43:51,000 --> 00:43:53,000
 understanding what He says.

712
00:43:53,000 --> 00:43:55,000
 "Hey, here's where life is.

713
00:43:55,000 --> 00:43:57,000
 There's not life there.

714
00:43:57,000 --> 00:43:59,000
 The Christians are going to tell you

715
00:43:59,000 --> 00:44:01,000
 there's life there, and they're wrong.

716
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:03,000
 You're going to find death

717
00:44:03,000 --> 00:44:05,000
 and divorce

718
00:44:05,000 --> 00:44:07,000
 there.

719
00:44:07,000 --> 00:44:09,000
 But if you go this way, as a stranger,

720
00:44:09,000 --> 00:44:11,000
 as an alien, as a weirdo,

721
00:44:11,000 --> 00:44:13,000
 as someone who's out of his mind

722
00:44:13,000 --> 00:44:15,000
 for the sake of the Gospel,

723
00:44:15,000 --> 00:44:17,000
 you're going to find life

724
00:44:17,000 --> 00:44:19,000
 in Jesus Christ alone.

725
00:44:19,000 --> 00:44:21,000
 Why wouldn't you do that?

726
00:44:21,000 --> 00:44:23,000
 If you didn't prioritize time with Him today,

727
00:44:23,000 --> 00:44:25,000
 you're going to wake up tomorrow,

728
00:44:25,000 --> 00:44:27,000
 I beg of you

729
00:44:27,000 --> 00:44:29,000
 to prioritize for the next 30 days.

730
00:44:29,000 --> 00:44:31,000
 Take a 30-day challenge.

731
00:44:31,000 --> 00:44:33,000
 If you hear this anywhere you are in the world,

732
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:35,000
 I want to challenge you

733
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:37,000
 to 30 days

734
00:44:37,000 --> 00:44:39,000
 of spending the first 30 minutes

735
00:44:39,000 --> 00:44:41,000
 of every single day,

736
00:44:41,000 --> 00:44:43,000
 not 5 days a week, 7 days a week,

737
00:44:43,000 --> 00:44:45,000
 the first 30 minutes,

738
00:44:45,000 --> 00:44:47,000
 I want you to carve out for Jesus.

739
00:44:47,000 --> 00:44:49,000
 If you're like, "I'm not a morning person,"

740
00:44:49,000 --> 00:44:51,000
 get some coffee or something.

741
00:44:51,000 --> 00:44:53,000
 But you prioritize

742
00:44:53,000 --> 00:44:55,000
 time with Jesus for the next 30 days.

743
00:44:55,000 --> 00:44:59,000
 If you're in on the 30-day challenge,

744
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:01,000
 I want you to raise your hand.

745
00:45:01,000 --> 00:45:03,000
 I want you to say, "Hey, I'm in on the 30-day challenge.

746
00:45:03,000 --> 00:45:05,000
 I'm going to do it with you.

747
00:45:05,000 --> 00:45:07,000
 We're going to be doing it right together.

748
00:45:07,000 --> 00:45:09,000
 That's why thousands of hands go up.

749
00:45:09,000 --> 00:45:11,000
 All of us, for the next 30 days,

750
00:45:11,000 --> 00:45:13,000
 we're going to start our life

751
00:45:13,000 --> 00:45:15,000
 with Jesus.

752
00:45:15,000 --> 00:45:17,000
 And we're going to ask Him, "What do we do?

753
00:45:17,000 --> 00:45:19,000
 And what do we not do?

754
00:45:19,000 --> 00:45:21,000
 And would you remind me that I don't belong to this world?"

755
00:45:21,000 --> 00:45:23,000
 As we worship Him now,

756
00:45:23,000 --> 00:45:25,000
 I want you to beg Him for that.

757
00:45:25,000 --> 00:45:27,000
 Ask friends to hold you accountable.

758
00:45:27,000 --> 00:45:29,000
 Ask others, text them.

759
00:45:29,000 --> 00:45:31,000
 Say, "Heaven, I text you every morning after I spent time with Jesus."

760
00:45:31,000 --> 00:45:33,000
 If you fall off the bus,

761
00:45:33,000 --> 00:45:35,000
 get back on.

762
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:37,000
 Let me pray.

763
00:45:37,000 --> 00:45:39,000
 Lord, we love you.

764
00:45:39,000 --> 00:45:41,000
 We do thank you so much for your example in Jesus Christ.

765
00:45:41,000 --> 00:45:43,000
 We thank you for the things

766
00:45:43,000 --> 00:45:45,000
 that you've taught us this evening

767
00:45:45,000 --> 00:45:47,000
 through your servant Peter.

768
00:45:47,000 --> 00:45:49,000
 For these two verses full of truth

769
00:45:49,000 --> 00:45:51,000
 that we can apply to our lives.

770
00:45:51,000 --> 00:45:53,000
 God, as friends gather

771
00:45:53,000 --> 00:45:55,000
 all over the country tonight

772
00:45:55,000 --> 00:45:57,000
 in El Paso and Tulsa

773
00:45:57,000 --> 00:45:59,000
 and Houston, the Woodlands, spring.

774
00:45:59,000 --> 00:46:03,000
 And my dear friends in Fort Worth,

775
00:46:03,000 --> 00:46:07,000
 God, would you renew our hearts

776
00:46:07,000 --> 00:46:09,000
 around the reality

777
00:46:09,000 --> 00:46:11,000
 that we don't belong to this world

778
00:46:11,000 --> 00:46:13,000
 in its current state.

779
00:46:13,000 --> 00:46:15,000
 You're going to perfect the world.

780
00:46:15,000 --> 00:46:17,000
 You're going to lay your kingdom here.

781
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:19,000
 We're going to live in paradise

782
00:46:19,000 --> 00:46:21,000
 forever with you.

