00:46:21,000 --> 00:46:23,000
 And Father, I know that there's friends

784
00:46:23,000 --> 00:46:25,000
 right now listening who have not trusted in you

785
00:46:25,000 --> 00:46:27,000
 through your provision

786
00:46:27,000 --> 00:46:29,000
 in Jesus Christ.

787
00:46:29,000 --> 00:46:31,000
 His death and resurrection is a payment for our sins.

788
00:46:31,000 --> 00:46:33,000
 So as we sing this song,

789
00:46:33,000 --> 00:46:35,000
 would your Holy Spirit

790
00:46:35,000 --> 00:46:37,000
 move into their hearts

791
00:46:37,000 --> 00:46:39,000
 and show them that you are the God,

792
00:46:39,000 --> 00:46:41,000
 the only God, the one true God,

793
00:46:41,000 --> 00:46:43,000
 the creator of the heavens and the earth

794
00:46:43,000 --> 00:46:45,000
 who have called them to know you.

795
00:46:45,000 --> 00:46:47,000
 Would you do that now, please, Lord.

796
00:46:47,000 --> 00:46:49,000
 In Jesus' name, amen.

